a.xlink:title: Checks if a coprocessor of a given id is present of not.
Sets a new value to the CPSR register.
Executes a coprocessor register transfer instruction (coprocessor instruction (1)).
Executes an MSR instruction (move data to CPSR/SPSR from an ARM register).
Returns the value of the SPSR register of the current CPU mode.
Sets the value of the SPSR register in the CPU mode passed in as a parameter.
Executes an MRS instruction (move data from CPSR/SPSR to an ARM register).
